org.openjdk.tools.javac.parser

类 JavacParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openjdk.tools.javac.parser.JavacParser
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Parser

    public class JavacParser
extends Object
implements Parser
    The parser maps a token sequence into an abstract syntax tree. It operates by recursive descent, with code derived systematically from an LL(1) grammar. For efficiency reasons, an operator precedence scheme is used for parsing binary operation expressions.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.

      • parseType

        public JCTree.JCExpression parseType()
        parses (optional) type annotations followed by a type. If the annotations are present before the type and are not consumed during array parsing, this method returns a JCTree.JCAnnotatedType consisting of these annotations and the underlying type. Otherwise, it returns the underlying type.

        Note that this method sets mode to TYPE first, before parsing annotations.

        指定者:
        parseType 在接口中 Parser
        返回:
        an expression for a type
